## 6. Premium Upgrades & Payment Gateway

Users can upgrade to premium for **₹25.00** to unlock the **Premium Color Palette** for lifetime drawing and **6 Months of Ad-Free Gameplay**.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Client JS
    participant RP as Razorpay SDK
    participant API as Backend Route

    User->>API: POST /api/payment/order (JWT auth)
    API-->>User: Returns orderId
    User->>RP: Razorpay.open(orderId, keyId)
    Note over RP: Opens checkout modal for payment
    RP-->>User: Returns payment_id & signature
    User->>API: POST /api/payment/verify
    Note over API: Verify: HmacSHA256(order_id + "|" + payment_id, secret)
    API-->>User: HTTP 200 (Success)
```

### Signature Verification
To prevent users from spoofing successful payments, the backend cryptographically verifies the payment signature using your Razorpay Secret:
```javascript
const hmac = crypto.createHmac('sha256', KEY_SECRET);
hmac.update(`${razorpay_order_id}|${razorpay_payment_id}`);
const expected = hmac.digest('hex');
if (expected === razorpay_signature) {
  // Grant Premium & update DB
}
```

